{"id": 1889, "genre": 1000, "title": "如果说公司也会遭遇“中年危机”，它们发作起来可能都有哪些表现？", "description": "企业中危起来，和人们遇到瓶颈的样子还真有点像。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 5527, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709051115075ujmvhKOgL9FbGCM.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-05T17:00:09Z", "questions": [{"id": 2918, "title": "如果说公司也会遭遇“中年危机”，它们发作起来可能都有哪些表现？", "content": "如果说公司也会遭遇“中年危机”，它们起来可能都有哪些表现？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 233765, "content": "年轻化营销，启用流量明星代言、蹭热点话题", "image": "img/option/option/20170905111628OuTXnS1qINiYZbRL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233767, "content": "跨界开店，同时涉足酒店、餐饮、日用品领域", "image": "img/option/option/201709051116597EF0yOWSvwpqQXV3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233768, "content": "风格换血，从大众实穿改走小众潮流路线", "image": "img/option/option/201709051118235uNyoqYpz87JZrRU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233775, "content": "换logo、slogan，顺势宣扬企业文化找点存在感", "image": "img/option/option/20170905112518PinJ0ETZYCaIoLOb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233776, "content": "产品升级，“把冷冻牛肉换成新鲜肉饼”类似的“全方位改革”", "image": "img/option/option/20170905112543O2n9hvVHIgwpEBWl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233777, "content": "开发新型业态，速溶咖啡品牌不卖咖啡，而是提供第三空间", "image": "img/option/option/201709051126111G7IbVaFRwZUr32u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233778, "content": "与其他品牌合作，推出联名款、限量款", "image": "img/option/option/20170905112641WEsN0DGnV6S42Urh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233779, "content": "建立热心公益/慈善人设，比如每罐面膜收益所得用来救助一只丹顶鹤", "image": "img/option/option/20170905112706QMBoTi56W8LACVtm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233780, "content": "推出改走亲民路线的子品牌，或者推出便宜的“新定价”", "image": "img/option/option/20170905112808VEDOInLKojzJeiq3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233781, "content": "推出改走贵族路线的子品牌，并悄悄隐去背后原品牌的身影", "image": "img/option/option/201709051130250H4YCuhGfypWd3Vr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233782, "content": "开始养生，不管原来干啥的，都装修北欧风店铺搞起健康轻食", "image": "img/option/option/20170905113154LCzNFHEdfPs1kYQV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}